On 6/13/03 12:25 PM, "Juan Valdez" <whistlingtin(-at-)hotmail.com> wrote:

> Quick question: What is the trick to remove the chrome trim rings around the
> headlights on a '73 Westy? I have removed the screws, and they don't want to
> budge.

The rings are just plastic so be careful. It's just stuck on from sitting
there for so long. Put something in the hole at the bottom and gently pry.

